\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 14, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104mmc1665702755696.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mmc1665702755696.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/mmc1665702755696.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"mmc1665702755696\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Retrieves a specified document from storage.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__topic_d127466e1_d127467e1_d127468e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__p_d127469e1_d127470e1_d127471e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword apiname\">uniface.datastore.get</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DocId</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__p_d127472e1_d127473e1_d127474e1\">Example:\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp')</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__section_w1406ab1b5b3_w1407ab1b5_w1408ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747266e73\">Arguments </h2>\n<dl class=\"dl parml\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__parml_q1c_2qb_dwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt pt dlterm\">DocId</dt>\n<dd class=\"dd pd\">The identifier of the document that you want to retrieve.</dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__section_w1409ab1b5b5_w1410ab1b5_w1411ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747266e91\">Return Value</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__p_d127484e1_d127485e1_d127486e1\">Returns a JavaScript Promise object. If the promise is\n        resolved, the specified document is returned as an object. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mmc1665702755696_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__codeblock_f4w_gqb_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">{\n \"_id\": \"songs_dsp\",\n \"_rev\": \"1-A6157A5EA545C99B00FF904EEF05FD9F\"\n \"title\": \"Rock and Roll Heart\",\n}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Otherwise, an error is returned.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__section_rh2_1rv_1dc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d747266e106\">Example: Using get()</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__p_d127493e1_d127494e1_d127495e1\">Assuming the data has been stored in a local database\n        under the <code class=\"ph codeph\">_id</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">songs_dsp</code>, the following code retrieves the data from local storage, and\n        loads it into the current DSP instance:</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104mmc1665702755696_html_1\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"mmc1665702755696__codeblock_g2q_pqb_dwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">// Look for the doc with id 'songs_dsp' and load its data to the current instance.\nuniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp').then(function (vData) {\n uniface.getInstance().setData(vData.title);\n}).catch(function (err) {\n console.log(err);\n});\nuniface.datastore.get('mydoc').then(function (doc) {\n // handle doc\n}).catch(function (err) {\n console.log(err);\n});</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529980\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529980\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "get() Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 14, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Retrieves a specified document from storage. uniface.datastore.get ( DocId ) Example: uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp') Arguments DocId The identifier of the document that you want to retrieve. Return Value Returns a JavaScript Promise object. If the promise is resolved, the specified document is returned as an object. For example: Explain this code { \"_id\": \"songs_dsp\", \"_rev\": \"1-A6157A5EA545C99B00FF904EEF05FD9F\" \"title\": \"Rock and Roll Heart\", } Copy Otherwise, an error is returned. Example: Using get() Assuming the data has been stored in a local database under the _id songs_dsp , the following code retrieves the data from local storage, and loads it into the current DSP instance: Explain this code // Look for the doc with id 'songs_dsp' and load its data to the current instance. uniface.datastore.get('songs_dsp').then(function (vData) { uniface.getInstance().setData(vData.title); }).catch(function (err) { console.log(err); }); uniface.datastore.get('mydoc').then(function (doc) { // handle doc }).catch(function (err) { console.log(err); }); Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}